{{no footnotes|date=March 2013}}
In [[Greek mythology]], '''Cassotis''' (Κασσωτίς) was the [[naiad]] (a [[Pegaeae|Pegaea]]) who lived in the spring at the [[Oracle]] at [[Delphi]], dedicated to [[Apollo]]; the spring was named after her.

