's bugloss.JPG|125px|Viper's-bugloss]] || [[Viper's-bugloss]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.plantlife.org.uk/uk/discover-wild-plants-nature/plant-fungi-species/vipers-bugloss |title=Viper's-bugloss |publisher=Plantlife |accessdate=2018-07-06}}</ref> || ''[[Echium vulgare]]'' || Native |- | [[Fife]] || [[File:Corallorrhiza_trifida_02_mg-k.jpg|125px|Coralroot orchid]] || [[Coralroot orchid]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.plantlife.org.uk/uk/discover-wild-plants-nature/plant-fungi-species/coralroot-orchid |title=Coralroot orchid |publisher=Plantlife |accessdate=2018-07-06}}</ref> || ''[[Corallorrhiza trifida]]'' || Native |- | [[Glasgow]] || [[File:Cytisus scoparius2.jpg|125px|Broom]] || [[Common broom|Broom]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.plantlife.org.uk/uk/discover-wild-plants-nature/plant-fungi-species/broom |title=Broom |publisher=Plantlife |accessdate=2018-07-06}}</ref> || ''[[Cytisus scoparius]]'' || Native |- | [[Inverness-shire]] || [[File:Linnaea borealis.jpg|125px|Twinflower]] || [[Twinflower]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.plantlife.org.uk/uk/discover-wild-plants-nature/plant-fungi-species/twinflower |title=Twinflower |publisher=Plantlife |accessdate=2018-07-06}}</ref> || ''[[Linnaea borealis]]'' || Native |- | [[Kinross-shire|Kinross]] || [[File:Hierochloe odorata 2017-04-17 7718.jpg|125px|Holy-grass]] || [[Holy-grass]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.plantlife.org.uk/uk/discover-wild-plants-nature/plant-fungi-species/holy-grass |title=Holy-grass |publisher=Plantlife |accessdate=2018-07-06}}</ref> || ''[[Hierochloe odorata]]'' || Native |- | [[Kirkcudbrightshire|Kirkcudbright]] || [[File:Andromeda polifolia 001.JPG|125px|Bog-rosemary]] || [[Bog-rosemary]]<ref name=bogrosemary/> || ''[[Andromeda polifolia]]'' || Native |- | [[Lanarkshire]] || [[File:Epipactis leptochila Saarland 11.jpg|125px|Dune helleborine]]|| [[Dune helleborine]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.plantlife.org.uk/uk/discover-wild-plants-nature/plant-fungi-species/dune-helleborine |title=