ift]]<ref name=thrift/> || ''[[Armeria maritima]]'' || Native |- | [[Radnorshire]] || [[File:Gagea bohemica sl2.jpg|125px|Radnor lily]] || [[Radnor lily]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.plantlife.org.uk/uk/discover-wild-plants-nature/plant-fungi-species/radnor-lily |title=Radnor lily |publisher=Plantlife |accessdate=2018-07-06}}</ref> || ''[[Gagea bohemica]]'' || Native |}
