um ralphii|Karo]] ''Pittosporum ralphii'' **[[Pittosporum eugenioides|Lemonwood]] ''Pittosporum eugenioides'' **[[Pittosporum patulum|Pitpat]] ''Pittosporum patulum'' **''[[Pittosporum ellipticum]]'' **''[[Pittosporum virgatum]]'' **[[Pittosporum turneri|Turner's kohuhu]] ''Pittosporum turneri'' *[[Elaeocarpus hookerianus|Pōkākā]] ''Elaeocarpus hookerianus'' *Pōhutukawa **[[Metrosideros kermadecensis|Kermadec pōhutukawa]] ''Metrosideros kermadecensis'' **[[Pōhutukawa]] ''Metrosideros excelsa'' *[[Leptecophylla robusta|Pouteretere]] ''Leptecophylla robusta'' *[[Puka (tree)|Puka]] ''Meryta sinclairii'' *[[Laurelia novae-zelandiae|Pukatea]] ''Laurelia novae-zelandiae'' *[[Carpodetus serratus|Putaputawētā]] ''Carpodetus serratus'' *''[[Nothofagus]]'' sp. *[[Puriri]] ''Vitex lucens'' *[[Lophomyrtus bullata|Ramarama]] ''Lophomyrtus bullata'' *[[Metrosideros|Rātā]] **[[Metrosideros bartlettii|Bartlett's rātā]] ''Metrosideros bartlettii'' **[[Metrosideros robusta|Northern rātā]] ''Metrosideros robusta'' **[[Metrosideros parkinsonii|Parkinson's rātā]] ''Metrosideros parkinsonii'' **[[Metrosideros umbellata|Southern rātā]] ''Metrosideros umbellata'' *[[Brachyglottis huntii|Rautini]] ''Brachyglottis huntii'' *[[Knightia excelsa|Rewarewa]] ''Knightia excelsa'' *Ribbonwood **[[Plagianthus betulinus|Ribbonwood]] ''Plagianthus betulinus'' **[[Plagianthus regius subsp. chathamicus|Chatham Island ribbonwood]] ''Plagianthus regius'' subsp. ''chathamicus'' **[[Plagianthus regius|Lowland ribbonwood]] ''Plagianthus regius'' subsp. ''regius'' *[[Syzygium maire|Swamp maire]] ''Syzygium maire'' *[[Taraire]] ''Beilschmiedia tarairi'' *[[Tawa (tree)|Tawa]] ''Beilschmiedia tawa'' *[[Weinmannia silvicola|Tōwai]] ''Weinmannia silvicola'' *[[Coprosma repens|Taupata]] ''Coprosma repens'' *[[Pouteria costata|Tawāpou]] ''Pouteria costata'' *[[Alectryon excelsus|Titoki]] ''Alectryon excelsus'' *[[Rapanea salicina|Toro]] ''Rapanea salicina'' *[[Melicope ternata|Wharangi]] ''Melicope ternata'' *[[Entelea arborescens|Whau]] ''Entelea aborescens'' (corkwood)
